            <li><strong>Cool Soundtrack:</strong> Original music tracks with a winter vibe that perfectly complements the gameplay</li>
            <li><strong>Seasonal Challenges:</strong> Unique mechanics and obstacles specifically designed for the winter theme</li>
            <li><strong>Smooth Gameplay:</strong> The same responsive controls you love from the original Geometry Dash</li>
            <li><strong>Atmospheric Effects:</strong> Visual effects that enhance the winter atmosphere without affecting performance</li>
          </ul>
          
