          <p>Geometry Dash SubZero maintains the core one-button control system. Press spacebar, click the mouse, or tap the screen to jump. Your character automatically moves forward, and you need to time your jumps perfectly to navigate through the icy obstacles and complete each level. The fundamental gameplay is familiar, but the new level designs provide fresh challenges.</p>
          
