          <p>The levels in SubZero are specifically designed with the winter theme in mind. Expect frozen platforms, icy spikes, and obstacles that fit the cool aesthetic. The difficulty progression is well-balanced, starting easy and gradually introducing more complex challenges. Each level feels like a journey through a frozen landscape.</p>
          
