          <h2 id="difficulty">Difficulty and Progression</h2>
          <p>SubZero offers a good difficulty curve suitable for both new and experienced players. Early levels teach you the basics with simple jumps and straightforward obstacles. As you progress, new mechanics are introduced and the challenges become more intense. The difficulty ramps up gradually, ensuring a smooth learning curve.</p>
          
          <h2 id="tips">Tips for Success in SubZero</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Pay attention to the icy visual cues for upcoming obstacles</li>
            <li>Listen to the winter-themed music to anticipate level patterns</li>
