          <p>While SubZero uses the same core mechanics as the original Geometry Dash, it offers a completely different experience. The winter theme, new levels, and unique music create a fresh challenge. If you're looking for variety in the Geometry Dash franchise, SubZero is an excellent choice.</p>
          
